project_descr: The programme aims to build on successful experiences with introducing  Integrated Water Resources Management (IWRM) in Kazakhstan and to promote transboundary dialogue and sustainable water resources management in Central Asia (CA).

outputs.output_descr: Regional Dialogue, IWRM Governance and Sector Capacity Building – Reg. component of the IWRM Programme for CA, aimed at program coordination, supporting regional IWRM activities & capacity building and addressing climate change and adaptation under IWRM

Developing and implementing Integrated Water Resources Management Strategies in Kyrgyzstan - national component of IWRM Programme for CA, supporting the government to develop &implement national IWRM and water efficiency strategies.

Developing and implementing Integrated Water Resources Management Strategies in Tajikistan - national component of IWRM Programme for CA, supporting the government to develop &implement national IWRM and water efficiency strategies.

Transboundary dialogue in the Ili-Balkhash River Basin - national component of IWRM Programme for CA, to support the government to foster transboundary dialogue and enhance cooperation with China for improved management of the shared river basin

project_title: promoting iwrm and fostering transbound. dialogue in ca
